OL,3,CPSNI to establish anti-racist police
OL,4,Cservice in the wake of recent violence
OL,6,FThe PSNI has acknowledged the hurt
OL,7,Fcaused to ethnic minorities by past
OL,8,Fpolice failings, including the
OL,9,Fhandling of local Black Lives Matter
OL,10,Fprotests.
OL,12,FIt comes as the force unveiled a new
OL,13,Ffive-year racism and ethnicity action
OL,14,Fplan in the wake of recent racist
OL,15,Fviolence in Northern Ireland.
