OL,3,CPSNI to establish anti-racist police
OL,4,Cservice in the wake of recent violence
OL,6,FThe new plan seeks to create an "anti-
OL,7,Fracist police service", rebuild trust
OL,8,Fwith communities following what they
OL,9,Fhave called "historical injustices",
OL,10,Fand increase the representation of
OL,11,Fethnic minorities within the police
OL,12,Fforce.
OL,14,FIn June, disorder in Ballymena was
OL,15,Fdescribed by a senior PSNI officer as
OL,16,F"racist thuggery, pure and simple".
