OL,3,CPSNI to establish anti-racist police
OL,4,Cservice in the wake of recent violence
OL,6,FMeanwhile last August, 349 race-
OL,7,Frelated incidents were recorded by
OL,8,Fpolice, twice the previous monthly
OL,9,Fhigh, and those are just the ones
OL,10,Freported.
OL,12,FMany of these incidents happened in
OL,13,Fsouth Belfast, Northern Ireland's most
OL,14,Fmulticultural constituency.
OL,16,FLocal community activist Takura Makoni
OL,17,Fhas been the victim of racist
OL,18,Fgraffiti, death threats and more;
OL,19,Fnobody has been convicted to date.
