OL,3,CPSNI to establish anti-racist police
OL,4,Cservice in the wake of recent violence
OL,6,FHe said: "Are we safe when we call the
OL,7,Fpolice? Do they respond? After they
OL,8,Frespond, do they follow up? Do they
OL,9,Fmake us feel that they are concerned
OL,10,Fabout what happened to us?
OL,12,F"These are the concerns anybody has.
OL,13,FIt's not about whether you're a
OL,14,Fmigrant. Nobody is looking for special
OL,15,Fattention from the police.
